/*Intuition :-
    Proshner moddhe emon pair count korar jonno bola hoise jekhane {CurrSum = TotalSum - (a1+a2)} 
    er value l theke boro ba shoman ar r theke chuto ba shoman hobe .

    --> l <= CurrSum <= r 
    --> l <= TotalSum - (a1+a2) <= r 
    --> l - TotalSum <= TotalSum - (a1+a2) - TotalSum <= r - TotalSum 
    --> l - TotalSum <= -(a1+a2) <= r - TotalSum [Multiply -1 on both side .]
    --> TotalSum - l >= a1+a2 >= TotalSum - r ..................(i)

    Ekhon problem er statement holo emon kotto gula pair ache jader summation er value
    TotalSum-l theke Chuto ba shoman and TotalSum-r theke Boro ba shoman.
    Duita value khuje ber korar problem removal er jonne ekta value ke constant dhore nibo.

    Form equation (i),
    --> TotalSum - l >= a1+a2 >= TotalSum - r .
    --> TotalSum - l - a1 >= a2 >= TotalSum - r - a1 .

    Ekhon amader kaaj onek sohoj , Emon a2 gula khuje ber korte hobe jader value
    TotalSum - r - a1  theke boro ba shoman ar TotalSum - l - a1 theke chuto ba shoman . 
    Er jonne C++ er inbuilt BinarySearch Function amra use korbo .
*/

void giveMeMyGloryBack() {
    ll n , l , r ; cin >> n >> l >> r ; vll vec(n) ; ll ans = 0LL ;
    tamjid(n) cin >> vec[i] ; nsort(vec) ; ll sum = Sum(vec) ;

    tamjid(n-1){
        ll low = lower_bound(vec.begin()+i+1,vec.end(),(sum-r-vec[i]))-vec.begin() ;
        ll high = upper_bound(vec.begin()+i+1,vec.end(),(sum-l-vec[i]))-vec.begin() ;
        ans += (high-low);
    }

    cout << ans << endl ;
}
